{"title":"山歌好唱口好开（两首）","authors":["严辰"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":5,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌好唱口好开（两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌好唱口好开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说山歌好唱口难开？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说樱桃好吃树难栽？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说白米饭好吃田难种？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说鲜鱼好吃网难挨？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快马加鞭大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风吹起好痛快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天也宽来地也宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌好唱口好开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户搞绿化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万紫千红扑面来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国变成大花园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"樱桃好吃树好栽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修堤筑坝兴水利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕干旱和水灾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处新秧绿油油，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白米饭好吃人人爱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大小水库满天星，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池塘泡子明镜开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷花谢了芦花白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜鱼好吃网好挨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕你风刮卜奎（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别提起“风刮卜奎”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起从前活受罪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小窝棚风刮跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹绿苗像水推，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无根的枯蓬滴溜溜转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人的心儿粉粉碎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今咱们当了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再不怕你风刮卜奎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宅旁路旁种果树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原栽上防护林带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全区绿化又香化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微风吹得百花开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架起风车快快转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为咱碾米又戽水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风不敢再逞凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低头听咱来指挥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改造自然人胜天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风调雨顺日子美。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）齐齐哈尔旧称卜奎，常年多风。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}